The paper deals with image domain adaptation and style transfer, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The authors also mention the use of a domainness variable to guide the model, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its model on benchmark datasets for semantic segmentation (cs.GR) and style generalization (cs.MM).
